      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The mechanical integrity is bolstered by a documented Vanos service and rear subframe reinforcement, addressing the platform's known structural requirements. The chassis retains its precision with a limited-slip differential and refreshed suspension bushings. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the powertrain delivers a linear power band and exceptional throttle response. A mechanically sound icon optimized for performance and engagement.",
