    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presented here is a meticulously maintained example that strikes the perfect balance between a reliable daily driver and a pride-of-ownership weekend car. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, though a close inspection will reveal minor stone chips and light surface marks consistent with respectful use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the premium upholstery is free of tears or stains, showing only the gentle character creasing expected of high-quality materials. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the intuitive infotainment system, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle is in excellent health, having followed a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule. Recent service includes a fresh oil synthetic change, new brake rotors, and a comprehensive cooling system flush. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts with precision, offering a driving experience that feels tight and responsive. This car comes with a clean title and a full folder of service receipts, ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
