      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it's honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved over the years\u2014perfect for anyone who wants a reliable ride that's ready for its next big adventure! Everything runs smoothly, and I've made sure it's clean and ready for you to hop in. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a test drive!",
